<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Patch 37 (October 21, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Fixed a bug that would cause the visual effects for jungle buffs to disappear from Freia.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Patch 36.1 (October 7, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Fixed a bug which was causing the buff indicator circles to disappear off Freia.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 32.1 (July 17th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Blinding Speed (W)</b></li><ul><li>The movement speed bonus granted by the second cast of this ability no longer decays over time.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 32 (July 9th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Blinding Speed (W)</B></li><ul><li>Reduced the auto attack delay after using this ability to 0.3 seconds, down from 0.4.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 31 (June 17th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Wrath (R)</B></li><ul><li>Fixed a bug that was allowing the Fear component of this ability to affect Shapers under the influence of disable immunity effects, such as Blitz.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 29 (May 5th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Blinding Speed (W)</B></li><ul><li>The cooldown of this ability has been reduced to 9/8/7/6/5 seconds, down from 10/9/8/7/6.</li><li>The movement speed granted by reactivating this ability has been increased to 60%, up from 40%.</li><li>The bonus movement speed duration granted by reactivating this ability has been increased to 3 seconds, up from 2.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 28 (April 8, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Blinding Speed (W)</b></li><ul><li>The cooldown of this ability has been reduced to 10/9/8/7/6, down from 14/12/10/8/6.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 26 (Feb 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Gouge (Q)</li><ul><li>The range of this ability has been increased by 11%.</li><li>The 2nd activation bonus damage has been reduced to 50/90/130/170/210, down from 70/120/170/220/270.</li><li>The 2nd activation Power ratio has been reduced to 0.6, down from 1.2</li></ul><li>Blinding Speed (W)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 600, from previous value of 675.</li></ul><li>Crippling Blow (E)</li><ul><li>The range of this ability has been increased by 11%.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 16 (Oct 31, 2013)</h4><ul><li>Fixed a bug that was causing Freia's Crippling Blow (E) to not display properly.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 10 (August 23, 2013)</h4><ul><li>Base Movement Speed reduced to 380, down from 385.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 7 (August 02, 2013)</h4><ul><li>Basic attack range increased to 130, up from 95.</li><li>Base health regeneration increased to 9, up from 7.5.</li><li>Health regeneration per level increased to 0.85 per level, up from 0.65 per level.</li><li>Magic resistance per level increased to 1.25 per level, up from 1 per level.</li><li><B>Crippling Blow (E)</B></li><ul><li>The slow this ability applies has been changed to a flat 40% at all ranks, down from 25/30/35/40/45%.</li></ul><li><B>Wrath (R)</B></li><ul><li>The duration of the Fear applied by this ability has been increased to 1.5 seconds, up from 1.25.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 5 (July 18, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Rage Shaper (Passive)</B></li><ul><li>Freia's passive will now generate 2 stacks of Rage when she uses basic attacks on an enemy Shaper, up from 1 stack per basic attack. She continues to only gain 1 stack of Rage per basic attack against non-Shaper enemies.</li></ul><li><B>Gouge (Q)</B></li><ul><li>The secondary activation bonus damage on this ability has been reduced to 70/120/170/220/270, down from 80/130/180/230/280.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 3 (June 21, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Wrath (R)</B></li><ul><li>The fear inflicted by Wrath will now cause more consistent movement by affected target(s).</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 2 (June 13, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Wrath (R)</B></li><ul><li>Updated the visual effects of this ability to improve its readability.</li></ul><li>Fixed a bug with Freia's death voice over where it was being broadcast globally.</li></ul>